  "texts": [
    "CA networking protocols and architectures [35] enable IoT devices to communicate and share context effectively [36].",
    "These networking solutions optimize data transmission and resource allocation based on contextual factors [37,38].",
    "In summary, contextawareness is a key enabler for unlocking the true potential of IoT applications.",
    "By embracing stateof-the-art techniques for capturing and processing contextual information, IoT systems can offer personalized, adaptive, and efficient services across diverse domains, leading to enhanced user experiences and optimized RU.",
    "Research Challenges in CA IoT SystemsThese challenges span various dimensions, from data acquisition to security and interoperability, and require innovative solutions for seamless integration and efficient functioning of CA IoT."
